var PQA = global.get("PQA.Real_Time_Parameters", 'memoryOnly') || [];
var C2S = global.get("C2S.Implicit", 'memoryOnly') || [];
var DownHoleData = global.get('Process_data.DHS', 'memoryOnly') || [];

var date = new Date();

// Date
var year = date.getFullYear();
var month = date.getMonth() + 1;
var day = date.getDate();

//Time
var hours = date.getHours();
var minutes = date.getMinutes();
var seconds = date.getSeconds();

msg.payload = {
